---
title: Quick Start
description: Get productive with {{TOOL_NAME}} in 60 seconds
---

## Show help

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} --help
```

## Check version

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} version
```

## JSON output

Every command supports `--json` for scripting:

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} <subcommand> --json | jq '.'
```

## Dry run

Preview changes before applying them:

```bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} <subcommand> --dry-run
```

## Shell completions

```bash
# bash
{{TOOL_NAME}} --install-completion bash

# zsh
{{TOOL_NAME}} --install-completion zsh

# fish
{{TOOL_NAME}} --install-completion fish
```
